{{Han etym}}
Originally 𢱭. {{Han compound|手|𠦪|alt1=扌|ls=ic|t1=hand|t2=herbs}}, a hand holding herbs as a gift. 𣬓 and 𢫶 are variant forms showing the hands at the bottom.

